name: NOOB THE CUBE 2
description:
doom the cube has yet again kidnaped glue the cube!

and now its up to noob the cube to rescue glue the cube and get his girlfriend back!

CONTROLS!

arrow keys!

press "e" to jump into paintings!

press "w" and "s" to change the volume of the music!

FUN FACT!

you can press "p" so skip levels 1-4

PLEASE NOTIFY ME ABOUT ANY BUGS YOU FIND IN THE GAME!
